The initial image in medium 1 described by the column vector $I_1 = \begin{pmatrix} l_1 \\ \alpha_1 \end{pmatrix}$ is transformed into the final image in medium 2 described by the column vector $I_2 = \begin{pmatrix} l_2 \\ \alpha_2 \end{pmatrix}$. The transformation is accomplished by the refraction matrix $R_{12}$:

